ADDITIONAL NOTICES:

This project provides an installation script for the Silicon Motion USB Display
driver, which is proprietary software owned by Silicon Motion, Inc. The
proprietary driver is subject to its own license terms.

The EVDI (Extensible Virtual Display Interface) kernel module is developed and
maintained by DisplayLink and is subject to its own license (LGPL-2.1 for the
library, GPL-2.0 for the kernel module).

This installation script and documentation are provided as-is, without any
warranty or official support from Silicon Motion, Inc. or DisplayLink.
